author: veithen
msg: Updated the version of the org.apache:apache super-POM to 7. This solves two issues:
* It adds http://repository.apache.org to the repository list, so that Axis2 snapshots are downloaded from the right repository.
* It makes sure that all JAR artifacts contain the LICENSE file (and related files).

author: pderop
msg: Removed TemporalServiceDependency, but added a timeout attribute in the ServiceDependency annotation
